    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">1: Menu bar and General Toolbars</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;"><conditional-text type="IF" value="PROFESSIONAL"/><image src="1r.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> Menu bar</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-MenuBar-main.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="0,0,38,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Menu-File"><title>File menu drop-down</title></area><area shape="rect" coords="41,0,79,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/><area shape="rect" coords="82,0,120,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Add"/><area shape="rect" coords="123,0,161,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="169,0,207,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Filters"/><area shape="rect" coords="219,0,257,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-View"/><area shape="rect" coords="266,0,304,31" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Help"/></imagemap></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The commands in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">File, Edit, Filters, View, Dynamics, Help </text>menus are common to most CAD applications.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The commands in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add menu </text>are those that you use to build your <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text> model.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">General toolbars</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbars</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">above</text> and <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the graphics-area. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">All <text styleclass="VariableName">toolbars</text> are collapsed when you start <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">Click the icon to <text styleclass="VariableName">expand </text>and<text styleclass="VariableName"> collapse</text> each <text styleclass="VariableName">toolbar</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">General toolbars <text style="color:#ff0000;">ABOVE</text> the graphics-area</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-TOOLBARS-GENERAL-COLLAPSED-TOP.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>General toolbars above graphic-area</title><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="2,1,42,167" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="2,167,366,186" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-File"/><area shape="rect" coords="51,1,91,147" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="51,147,366,166" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Solids"/><area shape="rect" coords="100,1,140,127" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="100,127,366,146" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Run"/><area shape="rect" coords="149,1,189,107" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="149,107,366,126" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics"/><area shape="rect" coords="198,1,238,87" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="198,87,366,106" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="247,1,287,67" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/><area shape="rect" coords="247,67,367,86" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-Edit"/></imagemap></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">General toolbars <text style="color:#ff0000;">BELOW</text> the graphics-area</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MD-TOOLBARS-GENERAL-COLLAPSED-BOTTOM.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>General toolbars below graphic-area</title><imagemap><area shape="rect" coords="2,19,43,135" type="topiclink" href="MD-Element-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="2,0,258,20" type="topiclink" href="MD-Element-Visibility"/><area shape="rect" coords="98,59,140,135" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-View"/><area shape="rect" coords="98,39,258,59" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-View"/><area shape="rect" coords="49,39,90,135" type="topiclink" href="MD-Selection-Filters"/><area shape="rect" coords="49,19,258,39" type="topiclink" href="MD-Selection-Filters"/></imagemap></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="ELSE"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Menu-bar with Commands, or Toolbars, or Both.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You can choose to show the commands with <text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">the:</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Menu bar and pseudo ribbon, </li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Toolbars only, or </li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Menu bar and Toolbars.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Edit-ApplicationSettings">Application-Settings &gt; Accessibility tab</link>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><image src="1r.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> Menu bar</para>
    <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-17-Menubar.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Menu bar and File commands]]></caption></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The commands in the <text styleclass="T_Menu">File, Edit, Filters, View, Internet</text>, and <text styleclass="T_Menu">Help </text>menus are common to most CAD applications.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The commands in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-FunctionBlocks" styleclass="T_Menu">Function-Blocks</link><text styleclass="T_Menu">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-KinematicElements" styleclass="T_Menu">Mechanism</link><text styleclass="T_Menu">, Geometry, MD-Solids, Visibility, Run, and Dynamics </text>are those that you use to build your <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text> model. Different menus are active with different editor-types.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">General toolbars</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">General toolbars</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">above</text> and <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the graphics-area. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">Toolbars</text> are collapsed when you start <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">Click the icon to <text styleclass="VariableName">expand </text>and<text styleclass="VariableName"> collapse</text> each <text styleclass="VariableName">toolbar</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">General toolbars <text style="color:#ff0000;">ABOVE</text> the graphics-area</para>
